{"type":"message","id":"6d76ddc0","parentId":"15e00fa4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T14:03:17.410Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 22:03 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请帮我搜索以下4个领域的最新动态（2026年3月）：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n每个领域搜索1-2条有价值的行业信息，整理成简洁的笔记保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n要求：\n- 内容要与道简网络科技的业务相关（To B企业服务、政企客户）\n- 信息要有时效性（2026年的最新动态）\n- 每条信息包含：标题、来源、要点"}],"timestamp":1774015397408}}
{"type":"message","id":"4a387866","parentId":"6d76ddc0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T14:03:24.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我搜索4个领域的最新动态（2026年3月），然后整理成笔记保存到指定文件。这4个领域是：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n我需要：\n1. 使用web搜索工具搜索每个领域的最新动态\n2. 整理成简洁的笔记\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n让我先搜索这4个领域的最新信息。我需要使用miaoda-web-search技能来搜索。","thinkingSignature":"77bfcd7f2dcea06b31b9a2dcfd240f44ae3d714569fd0eb3a6486317fe3dc59e"},{"type":"text","text":"我来搜索这4个领域的最新动态。首先使用web搜索技能来获取2026年3月的最新信息。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xrqy8fmtamsq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":108,"output":182,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":30692,"totalTokens":30982,"cost":{"input":0.0000324,"output":0.0002184,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.00368304,"total":0.00393384}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774015397410}}
